  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is well known fact that postoperative whole breast radiation therapy (RT) in left breast
      cancer patient can cause cardiac problem according to the exposed dose. In the several
      studies in other countries, it was repeatedly showed that RT on prone position can reduce
      cardiac exposed RT dose in left breast cancer. However, the effectiveness of prone position
      in RT is not studied in the Korean women have relatively small breast. The investigators
      planned this study to evaluate the real efficacy of prone position in Korean breast cancer
      treated with RT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
